.claude/
.codex/
# Cargo build artifacts. `**/target/` catches nested targets in any sub-crate
# (e.g. fixtures/downstream/target/, tools/integrity/target/). Keep the root
# `/target/` line for clarity; `**/target/` is the real guarantee.
/target/
**/target/
# Keep the root Cargo.lock tracked: this workspace includes binary developer
# tools, and release verification should use a reproducible dependency graph.
/.artifacts/
/.integrity-cache/
/.cache/
/guide/book/
*.profraw
*.log
/ci_output.txt
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.env
.env.local
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
# Nested Cargo.lock files from path-dependency fixture crates — none of the
# fixtures ship, so their lockfiles are cache, not source of truth.
fixtures/*/Cargo.lock
